page.title: 14SARAH'S TYPICAL DAY
page.content: Wednesday June 10th 1985 08.00am Got up & fed goldfish ate breakfast of Ricekrispies & coffee. 08.15 Got dressed,cleaned teeth got swimming gear out. 08.40 Headed towards school. 08.55 Bell went,took coat & shoes off & went to classroom for registeation lined up for assembly. 09.00 Assembly started hymns & prayers, after did group work,maths. 10.00 Coach came for swimming at Beverley baths. 12.00 Dinner time had sausage meat,potatoes,pudding was chocolate sponge. 1.10 Bell went for dinner playtime I did English Language. 2 .15 playtime played with Sara. 2.30 Finished English then wrote a story about a magic tree.
